title: Led Zeppelin - RetroActive Promo Box Set (2001) [FLAC]
description:
Led Zeppelin: RetroActive Promo Box Set (2001)

Mega Rare 2001 US promotional limited edition Warner/Retro Active label in-house publishing-only 40-track 3-CD set, each CD is housed inside a custom card wallet featuring a different black & white picture of different people holding different Led Zeppelin albums on one side & the track listing for that CD on the other. Also includes a 12-page picture booklet featuring a picture of each band member, intro from Cameron Crowe & discography, all housed inside a superb 5" x 5" numbered clamshell 'Zeppelin disaster' picture box. Only 2500 copies produced...
